Date: Fri, 24 Oct 2003 14:21:29 -0500
From: Brobson Lutz <bl@combsandlutz.com>

Are the Florida sources saying that the MRSA came from creatures from the
deep?
The commercial fishermen and the surfer were probably self-colonized
with MRSA, and a marine injury simply provided the portal of entry.
--
Brobson Lutz, MD, MPH
New Orleans
<bl@combsandlutz.com>
